  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2008-11-19",
    "date": "2009-01-07T19:28:08Z",
    "text": "Encourages the Department of State to place Vietnam on the list of \"Countries of Particular Concern\" for particularly severe violations of religious freedom.\n\nCondemns the ongoing and egregious violations of religious freedom in Vietnam, including the detention of religious leaders and the long-term imprisonment of individuals engaged in peaceful advocacy.\n\nCalls on Vietnam to lift restrictions on religious freedom and implement necessary legal and political reforms to protect religious freedom."
